import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET

def parse_xml(xml_file_path):
    """"""
    tree = ET.parse(xml_file_path)
    root = tree.getroot()
    node_names = []

    def visit_node(node):
        node_names.append(node.tag)
        for child in node:
            visit_node(child)
    visit_node(root)
    return node_names
